🧠 Loop Engine (core runtime)

S_{t+1} = \mathcal{W}(S_t, F_t)

with adaptive updates:

* F_t \leftarrow revised from feedback
* w_t \leftarrow confidence recalibration
* \alpha_t \leftarrow reversibility-aware step size

