⚙️ Modes (Horse Protocol embedded)

🟢 Ride Mode (mounted)

* high \alpha, high w
* action-biased
* used when:
    * pattern stability is high
    * reversibility acceptable

⸻

🔵 Walk Mode (alongside)

* low \alpha, dynamic w
* observation + model correction
* used when:
    * uncertainty rises
    * anomalies detected

⸻

🔴 Dismount Mode (hard reset)

* \alpha \to 0
* re-evaluate F entirely
* triggered by:
    * divergence
    * contradiction
    * failed predictions

