🧭 Governing invariants

1. Flow > Force
    * align before acting
2. Reversibility Gate
    * large \alpha only when rollback is possible
3. Confidence is earned
    * w must be updated from real feedback
4. Attractor ≠ destiny
    * all F are provisional

⸻

⚠️ Failure modes

* Runaway Current
    * bad F, high w, high \alpha
        → you get carried somewhere wrong fast
* False Calm Water
    * low signal mistaken for stability
* Over-Steering
    * fighting the flow → inefficiency
* Drift
    * too little \alpha → no progress

